# Vercel — must never be committed: Vercel's Build Output API treats a
# checked-in .vercel/output as a "prebuilt" deployment and skips the actual
# build step entirely, silently deploying whatever was built locally at
# commit time instead of building fresh from source + current env vars.
.vercel

